# INSTALLATION

These are the installation instructions for App::ShaderToy:

## Unix / Linux / Mac OS

    git clone https://github.com/Corion/app-shadertoy.git
    cd app-shadertoy
    cpanm --installdeps .
    perl Makefile.PL
    make

## Windows / Strawberry Perl

    git clone https://github.com/Corion/app-shadertoy.git
    cd app-shadertoy
    cpanm --installdeps .
    perl Makefile.PL
    dmake

